column29: Dex:TT1 and Dex:NTT constructs were produced as follows: TT1 and NTT CDS were cloned into a the donor vector (pDONR221) (Life Technology).  TT1, and NTT, were then introduced into the Gateway destination vector pEN-L4-pOp6M2-R1 which contain the pOp6 promoter that carry six copies of a lac operator sequence.
